Package: seuratConstellation
Title: Constellation Plot for Seurat V5 Objects
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Liangxian Developer
Maintainer: Liangxian Developer <liangxian@example.com>
Description: A pipeline-style toolkit for creating constellation plots from Seurat V5
    objects. Visualizes cell type relationships based on KNN graph analysis with
    customizable node sizes, edge widths, and color schemes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    Seurat (>= 5.0.0),
    ggplot2,
    ggrepel,
    dplyr,
    RANN,
    scales,
    grDevices,
    Hmisc
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    concaveman
Config/testthat/edition: 3
